      <title>印度尼西亚新首都或将免受普拉博沃预算削减的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-s-new-capital-may-be-spared-from-prabowo-s-budget-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管印尼总统普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 提出的多项社会计划均大幅削减开支，但印尼未来的首都很可能不会受到影响，其预算仍将保持完整。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-13/indonesia-s-new-capital-may-be-spared-from-prabowo-s-budget-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Feb 2025 07:35:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
